        [Eradiate radiative transfer model](https://www.eradiate.eu).
        
        The Pinttrs logo is based on 
        [Agus Nugroho](https://www.iconfinder.com/nugrohoagus)'s glass icon and parts of 
        the ``attrs`` logo.
        
